<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.3.1">
<l>veṉṟi māmaḻu vēntimuṉ maṇmicai maṉṉarai mūveḻukāl</l>
<l>koṉṟa tēvaniṉ kuraikaḻal toḻuvatōr vakaiyeṉak karuḷpuriyē</l>
<l>maṉṟil māmpoḻil nuḻaitantu mallikai mauvaliṉ pōtalartti</l>
<l>teṉṟal māmaṇaṅ kamaḻtara varutiru veḷḷaṟai niṉṟāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Lord, bearing the large victorious battle axe,</l>
<l rend="indent">who once killed the kings on earth three-seven times,</l>
<l>Grant me the grace of one way of worshipping</l>
<l rend="indent">your [feet with] rattling anklets,</l>
<l>[Lord] who stands in Tiruveḷḷaṟai where southern breezes come</l>
<l rend="indent">to aimlessly spread profuse fragrance,</l>
<l>Creeping aimlessly through the mango grove in the commons,</l>
<l rend="indent">coaxing open the buds of Arabian and wild jasmine.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
